        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "vehicle",
        "text": "This steam-powered vehicle has eight sets of axles, each with a pair of huge, spiked metal wheels that are independently powered and can independently shift up and down. This enables the engine to maintain a constant speed even over difficult terrain. On top of the vehicle sits a rotating weapon mount outfitted with a steelstone cannon.",
